reg_info.act_under: Municipality of Metropolitan Toronto Act   Loi sur la municipalité de la communauté urbaine de Toronto

content.content: 1. Ontario Regulation 949/93 made under the Regional Municipalities Act applies, with necessary modifications, to a by-law passed by the Metropolitan Council under subsection 150 (1) of that Act by virtue of section 73.1 of the Municipality of Metropolitan Toronto Act. O. Reg. 952/93, s. 1.
